{"tid":1995392,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國出現“甲殼類病毒”，蝦蟹死亡率高達80%","createTime":"2020-04-30T08:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T09:25:37.000Z","uid":122940,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"083fb060da14255593215ab13d1b45973cb3706e","tid":1995392,"uid":122940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:20:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/04/29/a102834849.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F04%2F29%2Fa102834849.html&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=59917796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/04/29/a102834849.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【新唐人北京時間2020年04月30日訊】除了中共肺炎（武漢肺炎）、非洲豬瘟，中國近期又添加鼠疫、甲肝等人畜疫情。日前陸媒報導，中國沿海至少11省市的蝦類養殖場流行高致死性的甲殼類病毒。<br />\n<br />\n陸媒《水產前沿雜誌》4月12日報導，今年春天南方蝦病高發，特別是華南的珠三角、汕尾、饒平、福建等地，局部地區出現連片發病排塘的情況，發病率高達6成。檢測結果都指向與「蝦虹彩病毒」高度相關。<br />\n<br />\n广告<br />\n<br />\n報導說，早在2014年，中國科研團隊就發現這種病毒，後來被正式命名為「十足目虹彩病毒」（DIV1）。這是一種高傳染性的病毒，不僅殺死蝦，還會殺死龍蝦和螃蟹等「十足目甲殼動物」。<br />\n報導提到，在中國沿海的11個省市中都發現了這種病毒，目前已知病毒在中國主要的蝦類養殖地區廣泛傳播，狀況緊急，且沒有特效藥處理，只能以預防為主。當蝦感染這種病毒時，蝦會出現變紅、空腸胃、黑腳等症狀，死亡率非常高，在養殖南美白對蝦和羅氏沼蝦可以達到80％以上。<br />\n日本《周刊郵報》（NEWSポストセブン）報導，一旦發生感染就沒有辦法解決，病毒會在幾天內擴散到整個養殖池。如果不將附近的池塘一併清除、抽乾，病毒傳播的速度將會非常快速。<br />\n報導還說，中國「甲殼類謎之病毒」疫情爆發的原因及其傳播方式尚不清楚，可能是藉由水作為傳播媒介。這種病毒目前不會傳染人，但不保證它不會如禽流感病毒般突變後傳染給人類。"},{"pid":"0cc53407841d20e6382a7908064bca5e9d96725e","tid":1995392,"uid":291465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:23:33.000Z","msg":"十災"},{"pid":"a035a58110cf0bdaf30431daef66e9f7977da263","tid":1995392,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:26:02.000Z","msg":"河水變血未？"},{"pid":"08c5cfb2630ced3c0810e7ee9a2f6fcdf2cee78a","tid":1995392,"uid":52946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:33:33.000Z","msg":"中國真係痴撚線可以殺盡所有生命體"},{"pid":"fd470e75a783ef1357a591b7bc43171ee694bb18","tid":1995392,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T09:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nub9UbP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnub9UbP.png&h=277e391e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/30/170639_aad4425f1d63afae666f99d5a5d3501f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F30%2F170639_aad4425f1d63afae666f99d5a5d3501f.png&h=85cd7def&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n留意日期<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b393f2a93e636bdfd0a625edd6d8e636bf6df4","tid":1995392,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T09:13:01.000Z","msg":"海陸空動物俾支那玩撚殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0da9c16d7a4a39cf504ac4d55d2f845ea4b3eb0","tid":1995392,"uid":122940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T09:18:56.000Z","msg":"中國乜嘢病毒都有"},{"pid":"8deec4331253593be82df8a3c9fcfcf6215fe0d2","tid":1995392,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T09:20:48.000Z","msg":"死左既蝦蟹 會點用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68d22992af41eb98b687bf17f9a0778f1b72a12","tid":1995392,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8deec4331253593be82df8a3c9fcfcf6215fe0d2","tid":1995392,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T09:20:48.000Z","msg":"死左既蝦蟹 會點用<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma